    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "While this sinister-looking weapon isn't inherently evil, its unsettling appearance and powers particularly appeal to those who revel in causing pain. A *grisly scythe* has a twisted thorny haft and a blade that appears to be rusted, but it functions as a *+1 striking wounding scythe*.",
        "level": 9,
